name: Twitter CEO Floki
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.

description.en:
a meme token that operates within the Binance Smart Chain ecosystem, and its fate is not subject to any individual's control.

Thanks to its community-driven nature, the popularity of $FLOKICEO is on the rise. Even Elon Musk has expressed his fondness for Floki, and he recently offered me the CEO position at Twitter. With the help of the community and Elon Musk's support, we believe that $FLOKICEO has the potential to become as successful as other popular meme tokens like Shib and Floki, and will soon gain widespread recognition across the globe.
